## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not capture all perspectives or the most recent industry trends. Additionally, salary data and job growth projections can vary based on geographic location and specific industry sectors. Further research, including interviews with industry professionals and analysis of recent market reports, could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the software engineering career landscape.